IMPORTANT — THIRD-PARTY TOOL RESTRICTION
=========================================

ProcessGuard MCP optionally integrates with Microsoft Sysinternals tools
(Process Explorer, Autoruns/Autorunsc). These tools are NOT part of this
software and are NOT covered by this licence.

Microsoft Sysinternals tools are subject to the Microsoft Software Licence
Terms for Sysinternals:
https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/sysinternals/license-terms

Those terms prohibit redistribution and use in commercial products without
a separate agreement with Microsoft. As a result:

  IF YOUR USE OF THIS SOFTWARE INVOLVES SYSINTERNALS TOOLS (i.e. you have
  configured procexp_path or autoruns_path), YOU MAY NOT USE THIS SOFTWARE
  AS PART OF A COMMERCIAL PRODUCT OR MONETISED SERVICE without first
  obtaining the appropriate rights from Microsoft.

This restriction does not affect use of ProcessGuard MCP without Sysinternals
integration (Stages 0, 3, 4, and 5 do not require Sysinternals tools).

For clarity: this restriction originates from Microsoft's licence for
Sysinternals — not from the author of this software.
